# monicPolynomial

- _monicPolynomial(p)_

Answer the monic polynomial of _p_,
a non-zero univariate polynomial in which the leading coefficient is equal to one.

```
>>> Polynomial[1 3 2]
>>> .monicPolynomial
Polynomial[1/2 3/2 1]
```

* * *

See also: gcd, Polynomial, UnivariatePolynomial

